relation: Even though he's far, far away, he loves his family dearly. He's trying hard to make it home for your birthday. Cross your fingers!
He's watchin' y'all. Don't even think about gettin' near his beautiful daughter, or it's th' eye lasers fer you!
It can stop time and drip all over you. Go figure.
